### James D. Hamilton

For individuals sharing the same appellation, consult [James Hamilton (disambiguation)](/James_Hamilton_(disambiguation)). This isn't some casual acquaintance; this is *the* James D. Hamilton.

**James D. Hamilton**
Born November 29, 1954 (age 71)

*   **Academic Pedigree:**
